Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛米罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛米罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所向往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也追不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以甩下过去的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…向着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时间居然还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作和时间可没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始不想当杀手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天捡了一部坏掉了的录影机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想试试能不能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买部新的不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样多浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能用…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早去早回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想分开  想一直待在玲二身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还能回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是洗手不干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是逃之夭夭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  我真是老在拖你后腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是听说了哦  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个Phantom呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪我那些年轻的兄弟这么轻易地就被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必再演戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是拿着证据的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没话好说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你丑态毕露之前还是听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道这是上头要你干的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想找到黑幕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受的三次袭击都是克劳迪娅指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为克劳迪娅为了让你们加入Inferno费了多少心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不讨厌那些忠诚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那女人可不是值得你们效忠到这种地步的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被耍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  这位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是第一次在这里见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是个值得回忆的夜晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  到现在都快一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  哪个组织的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能高兴得太早哦  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们和赛斯联手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯我可不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排这事儿的可是克劳迪娅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们走投无路的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人突然跑来跟我们磋商
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们抢到500公斤的可卡因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事前的准备都做好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接应的人也安排好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跟我们说「要不要在洛杉矶大闹一番呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件是等这事平息后  梧桐组要通过她介绍加盟Inferno
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们最初也不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但知道那个女人的立场之后还是想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人很想在Inferno里拥有能当自己后盾的集团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直独来独往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一辈子都没有出人头地的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前都是从别的地方购入货物那都是胡说八道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐组的整个市场都是我在这一年里抢来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以欠你们的可卡因为本钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  克劳迪娅把赛斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有个呆子在那起事件中受到了牵连呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的那个赛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急变  赛斯背叛组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Phantom去袭击了Inferno的货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织现在正全力搜索这两人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都还没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有证明自己的清白  夺回Ein的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话该明白吧  这东西的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都和她有关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我们受伤  流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有点头绪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗？  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来闻名天下的Phantom也过不了美人关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  这件事还有后文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人到最后还想把志贺和我抛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接掌握梧桐组啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边为灭口把我们干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边还趁乱把自己的对手也消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她腹黑到什么程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？那个女人把我们当踏板了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不管Inferno什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺负成这样还不做声我就不叫梧桐大辅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信  我可不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这卑鄙下流的盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上车  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱…爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到  你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么？  爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是从前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是个Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno马上就会来追杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次会彻底地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管现在还是从前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯·玛斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐组  克劳迪娅·玛秋奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有Inferno的艾扎克·怀斯梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离间三者使他们互相猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将曾经陷害过你的人一个又一个地送进地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相由我的安排传达给了Inferno
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将会立刻采取行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀叛徒克劳迪娅·玛秋奈以及其心腹Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织要除掉我？这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  通过了吗  入学考试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想立刻告诉叔叔  直接过来没打扰您工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很辛苦吧  贸易的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  挺辛苦的  后天还得离开日本去进货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了啦  老麻烦您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是收您太多礼物的话  会让妈妈知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我约好朋友去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得开心点吧  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是离婚了  美绪也流着跟我和组长一样的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梧桐之鬼的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人对她心怀不轨的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的美绪就连自己都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是变了立场还是改了姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙都是我的妹妹  重要的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贺  这次是大生意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不能活着回国的话  到时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪小姐前进的道路  我志贺会一直看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  志贺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打中了肚子和肩膀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我吃了这两倍以上的子弹都撑过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修罗道才是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  到头来又只剩下我和你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么时候都是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么样的地狱  你都跟我一起闯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的胆量和你的智慧  不管什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  克劳迪娅那边如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno会干掉那个女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  我们梧桐组才是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno绝不会饶恕在那女人麾下的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno算什么  骗了我们的帐  让他们好好还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为这帮家伙送上一场追悼战  对吧志贺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们全都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再死一个  就能摆平这一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今再说什么或许您都不会再相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  志贺是真心地仰慕您的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将造反的人清除掉表明了梧桐组的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno就由我来帮你们搭线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贺先生  这样一来梧桐组就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖瑟培  我现在压抑不住想对你开枪的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对我开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我跟你还有商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以成为好朋友  志贺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳  你在哪啊克劳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪啊  在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少给我个借口吧  克劳迪娅·玛秋奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑吧  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真不腻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会腻的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曲子你就那么喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是最喜欢的人送的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来认为自己什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的人都理所当然拥有的东西我都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直认为自己不会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直待在玲二身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告  对决
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如这个世界不是无尽的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为有你活着


